Connie Inge-Lise Nielsen -LRB- born 3 July 1965 -RRB- is a Danish actress whose first major role in an English language film was a supporting role in The Devil 's Advocate -LRB- 1997 -RRB- ; Nielsen later gained international attention for her role in Ridley Scott 's Gladiator -LRB- 2000 -RRB- .
Her films include Mission to Mars -LRB- 2000 -RRB- , One Hour Photo -LRB- 2002 -RRB- , Basic -LRB- 2003 -RRB- , The Hunted -LRB- 2003 -RRB- , The Ice Harvest -LRB- 2005 -RRB- and Nymphomaniac -LRB- 2014 -RRB- .
She starred as Meredith Kane on the Starz TV series Boss -LRB- 2011 -- 2012 -RRB- and was a lead character in the second season of The Following .
She is set to play Queen Hippolyta in the upcoming 2017 film Wonder Woman .